{"tid":2449153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田飛龍回應葉國謙批「廢柴學者」：「忠誠廢物」非針對個別人，而是一種現象","createTime":"2021-03-16T12:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T14:27:47.000Z","uid":339805,"like":179,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"71340a570b0837bdc90875c5385f281957a53f65","tid":2449153,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"【獨家訪問｜田飛龍回應葉國謙批「廢柴學者」】<br />\n<br />\n民建聯葉國謙日前指全國港澳研究會理事田飛龍的「忠誠廢物」論具侮辱性，反斥田飛龍是「廢柴學者」。田飛龍接受《眾新聞》訪問時強調自己並不生氣，解釋「忠誠廢物」非針對個別人，而是一種現象。<br />\n<br />\n田飛龍的足本回應請留意今晚9點，YouTube首播眾新聞中國組。<br />\n<br />\n【眾新聞YouTube Channel】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37A1PMI&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=2d00c27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37A1PMI</a><br />\n【眾新聞中國組全面睇】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ruHgdj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ruHgdj&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=d9a1f41d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ruHgdj</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/1407298699613535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fposts%2F1407298699613535&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=06fd517d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/1407298699613535</a>"},{"pid":"4adae01445eb3c05589fd816fba7e898b9f1d709","tid":2449153,"uid":103207,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"我唔係指個人，你地全部都係垃圾"},{"pid":"109391f0a9c8467ea45c1a3cb811f3520b00eeda","tid":2449153,"uid":25316,"like":342,"dislike":0,"score":342,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQKQ6pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQKQ6pZ.jpg&h=3fe6d695&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c28b482dd4875f59664cfc7462cb261e7e97367e","tid":2449153,"uid":33848,"like":48,"dislike":0,"sc